      "message": "BTW - I'm looking at these hacks I had to put in to remove sonar squid rule.\n\"Preconditions\" and logging arguments should not require evaluation (squid:S2629)\n\nHere is an example in another file that particular sonar was raised:\n               logger.info(\"get attribute error retrieving {}: {}\", pipRequest.getAttributeId().stringValue(),\n                                pipResponse.getStatus());\n\nand another example:\n                logger.info(\"No value for {}\", pipRequest.getAttributeId().stringValue());",
